data.description: Beautiful 2 story home, boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and a loft ready for bedroom conversion. Walk in to a stunning open living room, with one bedroom and a 3/4 bathroom situated downstairs.  Ample size family room and kitchen lead to backyard. Upstairs large primary suite boasts walk in closet, dual sink bathroom and ceiling fan.  This stunning home is located near shopping, dining and much more.
